1. *Džeri* mi je ugodno društvo. (I find *džeri* pleasant company.)
2. Često se vidjamo sa *džerima*. (We often meet with *džeri*.)
3. *Džerima* smo se obradovali. (We were delighted with *džeri*.)
4. *Džerom* smo se divili. (We were admiring *džeri*.)
5. *Džeru* smo obožavali. (We were worshiping *džeri*.)